'''Tropis-on-Varonat''' was a small [[City/Legends|city]] in the jungles of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Varonat/Legends|Varonat]]. Founded alongside [[Edgefields-on-Varonat]] circa [[250 BBY/Legends|250 BBY]]<ref name="Galactic Gazetteer: Hoth and the Greater Javin">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040325web|text=Galactic Gazetteer: Hoth and the Greater Javin|int=Galactic Gazetteer: Hoth and the Greater Javin}}</ref> by [[Human/Legends|Humans]] from [[Salliche/Legends|Salliche]], the city's population eventually grew to around several thousand individuals. It had a small [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] facility.

==Behind the scenes==
''[[The Essential Guide to Characters]]'' claimed in the entry for [[Talon Karrde]] that "Tropis-on-Varont" was a planet, rather than a city. This is contradicted by other sources.

